00:37:58,990 --> 00:37:59,740
Qi Da Cheng!

844
00:38:00,590 --> 00:38:01,260
Qi Dacheng,

845
00:38:02,400 --> 00:38:03,570
can you hear me?

846
00:38:04,400 --> 00:38:05,740
Does your ear feel like it's covered?

847
00:38:06,280 --> 00:38:06,930
No.

848
00:38:07,240 --> 00:38:07,930
Do you feel dizzy?

849
00:38:08,280 --> 00:38:08,780
No.

850
00:38:08,950 --> 00:38:09,740
Do you feel anxious?

851
00:38:10,400 --> 00:38:11,050
No.

852
00:38:11,760 --> 00:38:12,930
This is strange.

853
00:38:12,950 --> 00:38:14,410
Do a CT scan of the brain

854
00:38:14,430 --> 00:38:15,740
to rule out the possibility of epilepsy.

855
00:38:15,760 --> 00:38:17,010
What was the blood pressure you measured earlier?

856
00:38:17,030 --> 00:38:17,860
160.

857
00:38:17,880 --> 00:38:19,130
No history of high blood pressure?

858
00:38:19,430 --> 00:38:20,050
No.

859
00:38:20,280 --> 00:38:22,050
No high blood pressure, no anemia.

860
00:38:22,070 --> 00:38:23,260
He suddenly fainted.

861
00:38:23,280 --> 00:38:24,380
Has this happened before?

862
00:38:24,400 --> 00:38:25,450
No, never.

863
00:38:26,760 --> 00:38:28,090
Alright, I'll make some arrangements.

864
00:38:29,200 --> 00:38:29,860
Doctor,

865
00:38:30,200 --> 00:38:31,740
this won't affect my surgery, right?

866
00:38:32,680 --> 00:38:34,090
Let's first conduct a full check-up.

867
00:38:34,110 --> 00:38:35,570
The donor's family is causing a scene in the waiting room.

868
00:38:36,150 --> 00:38:38,260
How can we perform surgery without resolving the donor issue?

869
00:38:38,280 --> 00:38:39,610
Even if we can convince them,

870
00:38:40,280 --> 00:38:41,900
we can't take an uncertain risk.

871
00:38:42,110 --> 00:38:43,260
If the patient's condition is unstable,

872
00:38:43,280 --> 00:38:44,970
performing surgery would be irresponsible.

873
00:38:45,150 --> 00:38:47,050
Then we solve the problem.

874
00:38:47,880 --> 00:38:48,740
We've been preparing for five years,

875
00:38:48,760 --> 00:38:50,050
and today is the day.

876
00:38:50,630 --> 00:38:51,260
We've waited five years

877
00:38:51,280 --> 00:38:53,010
just to find the right donor.

878
00:38:53,200 --> 00:38:54,380
Now, there are only four hours left,

879
00:38:54,400 --> 00:38:56,260
and you want us to give up? That'd be the responsible thing to do?

880
00:38:59,590 --> 00:39:00,260
Mr. Chu,

881
00:39:00,430 --> 00:39:01,740
how's Qi Dacheng's condition?

882
00:39:01,760 --> 00:39:03,220
Have you found the cause of the fainting?

883
00:39:03,760 --> 00:39:05,340
From the reports we've gotten,

884
00:39:05,990 --> 00:39:06,820
everything is normal.

885
00:39:07,950 --> 00:39:08,860
Since that's the case,

886
00:39:09,720 --> 00:39:10,610
let's pause for now.

887
00:39:12,280 --> 00:39:13,490
I know no one's willing to give up,

888
00:39:13,510 --> 00:39:15,660
but Qi Dacheng's sudden condition

889
00:39:15,680 --> 00:39:16,660
is inexplicable.

890
00:39:17,070 --> 00:39:18,010
If we rush blindly,

891
00:39:18,320 --> 00:39:21,010
it could lead to regrets no one can fix.

892
00:39:23,760 --> 00:39:24,570
Let's call it quits for now.

893
00:39:24,760 --> 00:39:26,260
Everyone, return to your posts.

894
00:39:50,550 --> 00:39:52,050
You're not gonna give up too, are you?

895
00:39:53,590 --> 00:39:54,570
What are you thinking?

896
00:39:58,680 --> 00:39:59,490
Listen to me.

897
00:39:59,950 --> 00:40:01,260
No one's allowed to move Deng Lan's body.

898
00:40:01,280 --> 00:40:02,130
Wait for my call.

899
00:40:07,880 --> 00:40:08,660
Wait a moment.

900
00:40:11,240 --> 00:40:12,260
Qiao Yang, what are you doing?

901
00:40:13,030 --> 00:40:14,130
I just wanna ask one question.

902
00:40:14,150 --> 00:40:14,900
Stop being reckless.

903
00:40:14,920 --> 00:40:15,930
Who can guarantee

904
00:40:16,240 --> 00:40:17,860
that we'll have another donor?

905
00:40:18,320 --> 00:40:19,380
If we give up now,

906
00:40:19,400 --> 00:40:21,490
we're only giving up on these five years of preparation.

907
00:40:21,950 --> 00:40:22,970
What about Qi Dacheng?

908
00:40:24,280 --> 00:40:25,050
If we give up now,

909
00:40:25,070 --> 00:40:26,570
it could mean giving up on his entire life.

910
00:40:27,030 --> 00:40:28,380
We only have three hours left.

911
00:40:28,760 --> 00:40:30,050
In these three hours,

912
00:40:30,240 --> 00:40:31,610
if we can't solve Qi Dacheng's issue,

913
00:40:31,630 --> 00:40:32,410
I'll give up.

914
00:40:33,030 --> 00:40:34,050
But until then,

915
00:40:34,430 --> 00:40:36,090
I ask everyone to make sure to keep Deng Lan's body.

916
00:40:36,590 --> 00:40:38,090
Give Qi Dacheng one more chance.

917
00:40:39,240 --> 00:40:39,970
Please!

918
00:40:42,280 --> 00:40:43,090
Please!

919
00:40:47,110 --> 00:40:48,450
What did you have for breakfast?

920
00:40:49,280 --> 00:40:51,090
We were so focused on getting checked this morning

921
00:40:51,280 --> 00:40:52,260
that I didn't eat anything.

922
00:40:52,880 --> 00:40:53,900
Don't worry.

923
00:40:53,920 --> 00:40:55,260
Think carefully,

924
00:40:55,280 --> 00:40:56,700
besides the tests,

925
00:40:56,720 --> 00:40:57,700
did you do anything else?

926
00:40:58,630 --> 00:41:01,410
I came straight to the hospital for the check-up.

927
00:41:02,150 --> 00:41:03,050
I didn't do anything else.

928
00:41:04,280 --> 00:41:05,930
Do you have a family history of illnesses?

929
00:41:06,070 --> 00:41:06,740
What do you mean?

930
00:41:06,990 --> 00:41:08,740
Like high blood pressure, heart disease, etc.

931
00:41:08,760 --> 00:41:10,700
in your grandparents' generation.

932
00:41:10,720 --> 00:41:11,260
No.

933
00:41:11,510 --> 00:41:12,900
The CT scan result of his brain is out.

934
00:41:13,200 --> 00:41:14,090
Everything looks normal.

935
00:41:15,280 --> 00:41:16,450
Why are you so out of breath?

936
00:41:17,240 --> 00:41:18,090
There were too many people,

937
00:41:18,280 --> 00:41:19,380
and the elevator was too slow.

938
00:41:19,880 --> 00:41:21,090
I ran up the stairs in one go.

939
00:41:21,680 --> 00:41:22,900
I know you're in a hurry.

940
00:41:25,920 --> 00:41:27,380
Earlier, you said you dropped the report.

941
00:41:27,760 --> 00:41:29,300
You ran downstairs to pick it up?

942
00:41:29,590 --> 00:41:30,220
Move aside.

943
00:41:34,550 --> 00:41:35,260
Slow down.

944
00:41:36,510 --> 00:41:37,570
Watch your step.

945
00:41:39,880 --> 00:41:41,570
Is that when you started feeling itchy?

946
00:41:42,470 --> 00:41:43,380
And then fainted?

947
00:41:43,630 --> 00:41:44,740
Roll up your pant leg.

948
00:41:55,840 --> 00:41:56,930
I pressed the elevator button.

949
00:42:01,680 --> 00:42:02,410
What happened to her?

950
00:42:03,760 --> 00:42:05,260
I'll talk to you later.

951
00:42:05,680 --> 00:42:06,410
I'm free in a bit.

952
00:42:06,680 --> 00:42:07,260
Mr. Qin,

953
00:42:08,400 --> 00:42:09,380
let me introduce you.

954
00:42:09,630 --> 00:42:12,050
These three are evaluation experts from the consulting company.

955
00:42:12,070 --> 00:42:13,090
This is Mr. Qin.

956
00:42:13,110 --> 00:42:13,740
Hello.

957
00:42:13,760 --> 00:42:14,610
Qing, come.

958
00:42:15,280 --> 00:42:16,740
Take the experts for a tour first.

959
00:42:17,070 --> 00:42:18,610
I need to speak with Mr. Qin for a moment.

960
00:42:18,630 --> 00:42:19,380
This way, please.

961
00:42:22,240 --> 00:42:23,410
Consulting company?

962
00:42:23,950 --> 00:42:24,740
What's going on?

963
00:42:31,510 --> 00:42:33,610
I was the same reaction when I saw it.

964
00:42:35,880 --> 00:42:38,260
Mr. Chu and the two department heads are doing a face transplant today.

965
00:42:38,470 --> 00:42:40,930
Maybe we can discuss this when they return.

966
00:42:41,280 --> 00:42:41,860
No,

967
00:42:41,880 --> 00:42:43,260
it's better to talk about it now

968
00:42:43,280 --> 00:42:44,700
because they're not here.

969
00:42:44,950 --> 00:42:46,410
Otherwise, it might be a bit awkward.

970
00:42:49,550 --> 00:42:50,570
To be honest,

971
00:42:50,590 --> 00:42:51,740
in the past few months,

972
00:42:52,200 --> 00:42:53,570
dermatology and plastic surgery

973
00:42:53,760 --> 00:42:55,660
have been drifting further apart in performance.

974
00:42:56,200 --> 00:42:58,900
With the growing strength

975
00:42:58,920 --> 00:43:00,050
of our experts,

976
00:43:00,280 --> 00:43:01,740
our surgical capabilities are stronger than ever,

977
00:43:01,760 --> 00:43:03,180
but the performance keeps declining.

978
00:43:03,200 --> 00:43:04,900
Doesn't that warrant some serious reflection?

979
00:43:05,240 --> 00:43:07,010
Can I say this

980
00:43:07,030 --> 00:43:08,010
in front of Mr. Chu

981
00:43:08,430 --> 00:43:09,380
and the two department heads?

982
00:43:09,920 --> 00:43:11,490
It's the truth, so it's okay to speak openly.

983
00:43:12,630 --> 00:43:14,450
Since we're being honest,

984
00:43:15,150 --> 00:43:16,130
let me show you this.

985
00:43:17,400 --> 00:43:19,570
If we merge the staff and assets,

986
00:43:19,720 --> 00:43:21,740
we could reduce costs by at least 30%.

987
00:43:25,590 --> 00:43:28,130
Has Tang seen this data?

988
00:43:28,400 --> 00:43:30,050
This was arranged by Tang.

989
00:43:30,470 --> 00:43:33,260
Otherwise, would I have been able to invite these evaluation experts?

990
00:43:49,280 --> 00:43:50,130
Mr. Qin,

991
00:43:50,630 --> 00:43:51,970
take this and review it.

992
00:43:52,880 --> 00:43:53,970
I'll accompany the experts for now.
